# Task #131: MinUI.pak runs boot.d BEFORE the first nextui.elf of every boot, so the boot
# hook healing the GM root entry makes "artifacts exist before every root scan" an invariant —
# a partial card update can no longer hide the root row until the next full Lodor session.
desc boot.d hook installs the Game Manager root entry before the first root scan
invoke boothook
config paired
expect_exit 0
expect_file Emus/tg5040/LODORGM.pak/launch.sh
expect_file Roms/Game Manager (LODORGM)/Open Game Manager.gm
expect_file Roms/Game Manager (LODORGM)/Game Manager (LODORGM).m3u
# task #134 additions: pre-stage the LEGACY top-sorted folder + a user map.txt line;
# the boot heal must migrate the old folder away, install the NBSP bottom-sort alias,
# and keep the user line verbatim (merge, never clobber).
sdfile+ Roms/0) Game Manager (LODORGM)/Open Game Manager.gm
sdtext Roms/map.txt	Game Boy Advance (GBA)\tMy GBA Alias\n
expect_file_absent Roms/0) Game Manager (LODORGM)
expect_file_has Roms/map.txt	Game Manager (LODORGM)	 Game Manager
expect_file_has Roms/map.txt	My GBA Alias
expect_file_lines Roms/map.txt	2
